<title>Cheese and Mackerel Pie</title>
<outline>This recipe combines fish and potatos to make a fishy pie</outline>
<photo/>
<ingredients><ingredient>1 tin mackerel</ingredient>
                <ingredient> 4 potatos</ingredient>
                <ingredient> 2 oz grated cheddar cheese</ingredient>
                <ingredient> salt</ingredient>
                <ingredient> pepper</ingredient>
                <ingredient> paprika (optional)</ingredient>
                <ingredient>  Milk and butter for mashing potatos</ingredient>
</ingredients>
<instructions>Cook and mash the potatos. Put the Makerel in an oven proof dish. Season with salt, pepper and paprika. Cover with potatos. Sprinkle on cheese. Cook in oven at 150C for 30 minutes.</instructions>
